ttps://www.tsugi.fr\" class=\"subtitle-link\" target=\"_blank\">\n          Tsugi <b-icon icon=\"box-arrow-right\" />\n        </a>\n      </strong>\n\n    <p>\n      Toute la musique d'aujourd'hui… et de demain.\n    </p>\n\n      <strong>\n        <a\n          href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLWlqwXzikEuBZ-Edcr1_knBLU_AWBzHW_\"\n          class=\"subtitle-link\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n        >\n          Playlist YouTube <b-icon icon=\"box-arrow-right\" />\n        </a>\n      </strong>\n\n    <p>\n      Plus de 380 lives et documentaires électroniques réunis en une unique\n      playlist YouTube.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      <strong>\n        Testez vos connaissances musicales{{'\\xa0'}}!\n      </strong>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      De la chanson française aux années 80 en passant par le métal et les films\n      Disney, testez vos connaissances musicales à l’occasion de blinds tests en\n      ligne.\n      <ul>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://blinest.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"list-link\">\n            https://blinest.com/ <b-icon icon=\"box-arrow-right\" />\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </p>\n    <NextPrevBtn v-bind:nxtprev-list=\"nxtprevOnlineCultureMusic\" />\n    <Footer />\n  </div>\n</template>\n<style lang=\"scss\"></style>\n<script lang=\"ts\">\nimport { Component, Vue } from \"vue-property-decorator\";\nimport Header from \"@/components/Header.vue\";\nimport Menu from \"@/components/Menu.vue\";\nimport {BIcon, BIconBoxArrowRight} from \"bootstrap-vue\";\nimport NextPrevBtn from \"@/components/NextPrevBtn.vue\";\nimport Footer from \"@/components/Footer.vue\";\n@Component({\n  components: {\n    Header,\n    Menu,\n    BIconBoxArrowRight,\n    BIcon,\n    NextPrevBtn,\n    Footer,\n  },\n})\nexport default class OnlineCultureMusic extends Vue {\n  protected nxtprevOnlineCultureMusic =\n  {\n    BoolPrev: true,\n    BoolNext: true,\n    PrevImage: \"/thumbnail5.png\",\n    NextImage: \"/thumbnail6.png\"